{"tid":1650215,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"苦行撚出現了","createTime":"2019-10-13T00:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T00:31:17.000Z","uid":86509,"like":31,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"62cbd3b0e8d134a520ef1e380eaee2bc7595df55","tid":1650215,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:53:22.000Z","msg":"開始唔俾休息同快樂抗爭<br />\n講真休息時休息，抗爭時抗爭<br />\n休息嗰陣做下文宣不知幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快樂有時，悲傷有時，憤怒有時，平靜有時<br />\n人不嬲係咁運作㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n休息其實有咩問題？<br />\n日日吹大雞先係戇鳩<br />\n到九月個個要返工返學<br />\n星期一至五不嬲係休息<br />\n突然十月星期五遍地開花再加六日<br />\n三日抗爭咪開始休息囉<br />\n真係攰<br />\n而且急需人手幫手做外地文宣<br />\n都唔係話冇做嘢<br />\n<br />\n咁照計休息完星期六日會多返啲人<br />\n呢個係合理估計<br />\n同我想像一樣<br />\n但啲人又話唔係休息撚應該會仲多人<br />\n咁又有得鬧？？？<br />\n<br />\n真心日日抗爭行得通嗎？<br />\n全世界唔使返工返學？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住又成日暗串快樂抗爭<br />\n快樂抗爭同嘉年華兩個概念又混為一談<br />\n<br />\n正式進行苦行撚時代<br />\n<br />\n苦行撚出現了<br />\n<br />\n日本社運失敗原因<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%2F&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGe4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=c66f3e7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%2F&h=0b7fd4fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2/</a><br />\n<br />\n可是，後來，由於運動變成不是針對個別政策，而是轉向參與者追求突破自我，於是變成苦行式的，過度批判同行者的苦澀路線。作者解釋社運後來的發展：<br />\n「自我反省由於帶着強烈倫理色彩，忠於這些原則的運動者，會去攻擊不如自己認真看待運動的戰友，或是在沒辦法堅持原則的時候感到挫折。運動者無法對戰友採取寬容的態度，導致內部衝突和暴力，太着重於抽象的理念，容易陷入自以為是的危險」"},{"pid":"22dca6567a76e068455344c4556d07f13e8ec828","tid":1650215,"uid":186844,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:54:39.000Z","msg":"5毛收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da10f0b84361e6adb9ff8d5abde265dbc078563","tid":1650215,"uid":92299,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:54:51.000Z","msg":"Block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ead29f5bb418629fec205a5d0b5eaf4c2993e0","tid":1650215,"uid":201414,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"又一件休息撚 blocked"},{"pid":"b500b9f7d9b6659534e52bcaf4349bf063de3fd6","tid":1650215,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"22dca6567a76e068455344c4556d07f13e8ec828","tid":1650215,"uid":186844,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:54:39.000Z","msg":"5毛收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:56:53.000Z","msg":"最鍾意被人屈毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最早抗爭係我<br />\n勁多預計預測準又係我<br />\n勁多計劃又係我"},{"pid":"8dce4a6744add2666f9842c9582a4054860fcfec","tid":1650215,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91ead29f5bb418629fec205a5d0b5eaf4c2993e0","tid":1650215,"uid":201414,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"又一件休息撚 blocked"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:58:09.000Z","msg":"唔夠人講咪block<br />\n其實好正常<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c8d2c855d91bdf5fd91cf56366a4bf661c8593","tid":1650215,"uid":79182,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:59:34.000Z","msg":"唔想屌你<br />\n但真係唔好再休息<br />\n以後文宣要做足<br />\n最少兩星期宣傳"},{"pid":"c1cbfdd0f54cb26bccb257933532db6441b6246e","tid":1650215,"uid":266010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13