B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%2F&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGe4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=c66f3e7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%2F&h=0b7fd4fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2/</a><br />\n<br />\n可是，後來，由於運動變成不是針對個別政策，而是轉向參與者追求突破自我，於是變成苦行式的，過度批判同行者的苦澀路線。作者解釋社運後來的發展：<br />\n「自我反省由於帶着強烈倫理色彩，忠於這些原則的運動者，會去攻擊不如自己認真看待運動的戰友，或是在沒辦法堅持原則的時候感到挫折。運動者無法對戰友採取寬容的態度，導致內部衝突和暴力，太着重於抽象的理念，容易陷入自以為是的危險」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:25:22.000Z","msg":"攰就咪撚做啦<br />\n你仲出黎堅持開PO把撚咩<br />\n返屋企訓覺啦。"},{"pid":"f4a1e63ec196c9312f7d1efbb61667d0acebd373","tid":1650215,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:25:29.000Z","msg":"完全曲解日本社運<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"ac005ed6675ecd2d52ad579f959c36791362b29e","tid":1650215,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:26:07.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"da7e08f83467d6e3159e1ec3ba4a7718bf816b45","tid":1650215,"uid":242623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:26:30.000Z","msg":"Blocked"},{"pid":"dd9f25f0989156994d512fb38d367fac9e826701","tid":1650215,"uid":284264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:26:56.000Z","msg":"樓主無講錯wor<br />\n本來個運動就應該分和理非回合同勇武回合<br />\n<br />\n係最近亂晒咋嘛"},{"pid":"e4d00fd89ef5c1fbf3cc85b0a122ed80c26e0ac9","tid":1650215,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:27:01.000Z","msg":"風向又轉左去嘉年華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 